OL,3,CBrakes put on plans to fully extend
OL,4,CGlider to north and south Belfast
OL,6,FPlans to extend Belfast's Glider to
OL,7,FCarryduff and Glengormley have been
OL,8,Fpaused after the Infrastructure
OL,9,FMinister said it is not "economically
OL,10,Fviable" at the moment.
OL,12,FThe cost of implementing the proposals
OL,13,Fin full would cost more than #140m,
OL,14,Fbut just #35m is currently available
OL,15,Fto the Executive.
OL,17,FLiz Kimmins has said other
OL,18,Fdevelopments would still go ahead
OL,19,Fusing that money, including new stops
OL,20,Fat Queen's University and the City
OL,21,FHospital.
