OL,3,CBrakes put on plans to fully extend
OL,4,CGlider to north and south Belfast
OL,6,FHer department also intends to buy
OL,7,Ffour Glider vehicles that are powered
OL,8,Fby electricity.
OL,10,FOnce other projects are finished,
OL,11,Fplans to expand the Glider further
OL,12,Fnorth and south would be re-examined,
OL,13,Fthe minister said.
OL,15,FThe SDLP's Matthew O'Toole, who
OL,16,Frepresents south Belfast, said the
OL,17,FExecutive has "let down" people in the
OL,18,Farea.
