OL,3,CBrakes put on plans to fully extend
OL,4,CGlider to north and south Belfast
OL,6,FHe said: "The Minister's announcement
OL,7,Fthis morning is deeply disappointing
OL,8,Ffor those living in Carryduff and
OL,9,Fright across South Belfast.
OL,11,F"Carryduff is a growing area of nearly
OL,12,F10,000 people, and anyone who travels
OL,13,Falong the Saintfield Road regularly
OL,14,Falready know it's struggling to cope
OL,15,Fand needs a fast, frequent and
OL,16,Freliable public transport alternative."
OL,18,FHis frustrations were echoed by north
OL,19,FBelfast MLA Philip Brett who called
OL,20,Fthe minister's reasons for pausing the
OL,21,Fextension "utter nonsense".
